  "description": "Oceanic's boid school cohesion drives OHM's commune spread — when the school tightens together the commune tunes to unity; when the school scatters across the water column the commune detunes into a wide shimmer cluster. AmpToFilter bidirectional coupling: ocean_cohesion ↔ ohm_spread, amount 0.58. School and commune mirror each other's social geometry. Two collectives, one behavioral law.",
